PG| ***** 69 ***** |


NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The other point is that new suits by responder are forcing. On the other hand, contrary to what many players incorrectly believe, new suits by opener are not forcing. 1S was not forcing. Opener must reverse or jump shift to make a forcing bid.|
